1
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:11,320
Qi Beiyi shouted she is the Princess of Xuecang.

2
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:11,920
Right now,

3
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,160
she has been thrown into prison.

4
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,800
What?

5
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:18,020
Your Highness.

6
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:20,360
It's true that Ling Xuele is from Xuecang,

7
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,090
but how could she be a princess?

8
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,120
She now has a Nanping residency,

9
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,280
on the surface, nothing can be found.

10
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,600
Maybe

11
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,280
after a while, when His Majesty cools down,

12
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,340
he will let her out.

13
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,900
Besides, there's Consort Yu.

14
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,280
She'll be fine.

15
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,000
Consort Yu is like you,

16
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,930
neither of you knows her identity.

17
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,640
She really is a princess.

18
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,020
Only I can save her.

19
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:42,960
Report!

20
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:43,880
Speak.

21
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,680
Emergency military report for Your Majesty!

22
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,540
Yunqiu State suddenly attacked.

23
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:51,090
They have already reached the city gates.

24
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,400
Our soldiers were caught off guard.

25
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,280
I'm afraid

26
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,450
we can't hold on.

27
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,700
This King of Yunqiu

28
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,120
is too impatient.

29
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,060
I think he premeditated this.

30
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,760
Yunqiu

31
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,050
reached our city gates so quickly?

32
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:07,880
Then

33
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,760
what about the other cities?

34
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,570
It seems we have an internal

35
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,680
problem.

36
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:22,079
Notify King Jiyu immediately to send troops to help.

37
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:22,760
Wait.

38
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:25,840
Father.

39
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,880
King Jiyu departed less than half a day ago.

40
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,640
Now,

41
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,600
Yunqiu's army is at our borders.

42
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,320
They must have gotten the news earlier than us.

43
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:37,400
But King Jiyu hasn't sent any message.

44
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,760
So we need another plan.

45
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,250
Notify immediately

46
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,520
all officials to the hall for a meeting.

47
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,400
Yes.

48
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,280
Wait.

49
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,800
Don't bother.

50
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,360
Gather in front of the palace gates.

51
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:55,920
Your Majesty.

52
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,360
Madam.

53
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,280
Rest assured.

54
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,560
It's fine.

55
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,720
The Emperor has arrived!

56
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:23,960
Long live the Emperor!

57
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:30,680
Long live the Emperor!

58
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,120
Everyone,

59
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,800
please rise.

60
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,159
I think everyone knows

61
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,600
the situation outside the capital.

62
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,320
Just now,

63
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:44,840
I sent someone to notify Jiyu State.

64
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,320
I hope they

65
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,360
can send troops to reinforce us.

66
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,560
This crisis,

67
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,640
our Xuecang State cannot avoid.

68
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,680
Only by fighting to the death

69
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,730
can we win a glimmer of hope.

70
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,360
Does anyone

71
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,340
have any suggestions?

72
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,080
Your Majesty.

73
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:04,640
I have gathered over 50,000 soldiers in the city.

74
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,960
Although it's less than half of the Yun State's enemy forces,

75
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:09,680
our Xuecang soldiers are all brave and skilled in battle.

76
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,480
As long as before the Jiyu reinforcements arrive,

77
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,680
we hold the city gates,

78
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,880
repelling the enemy is not impossible.

79
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,690
This expedition

80
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,560
is extremely dangerous.

81
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,760
I hope Xuecang can receive

82
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,960
heaven's protection

83
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,650
and survive this disaster safely.

84
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,960
Report!

85
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,080
Your Majesty,

86
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,400
King Jiyu's army is only dozens of miles

87
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,560
away from the city gate.

88
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,640
We have sent someone to inform King Jiyu

89
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,840
of Xuecang's crisis,

90
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,170
but we haven't received any reply yet.

91
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,680
Warriors of Xuecang!

92
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,240
Now

93
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,280
is a matter of life and death for our country.

94
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,860
In such a national crisis,

95
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,090
we people of Xuecang

96
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,680
must fight to the death.

97
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,440
I

98
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:01,050
will lead the troops to battle myself,

99
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,640
and live or die with

100
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,880
our people.

101
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:06,440
We are willing to swear loyalty to Your Majesty

102
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,770
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

103
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,720
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

104
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:16,080
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

105
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,760
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

106
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,960
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

107
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,680
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

108
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,720
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

109
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,960
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

110
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:32,680
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

111
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,080
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

112
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:38,240
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

113
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,560
We swear loyalty to Your Majesty

114
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,560
and live or die with the people of Xuecang!

115
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,560
Girls,

116
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,200
follow me to support His Majesty.

117
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:53,840
Yes.

118
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,520
Charge!

119
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,760
Charge!

120
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,840
Hyah!

121
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,440
My lady.

122
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,080
Your Majesty.

123
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,010
Why are you here?

124
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,280
Didn't I tell you to leave the city?

125
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,159
Even in death,

126
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,960
I will die with you.

127
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,400
You...

128
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,890
The fall of Xuecang is inevitable.

129
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,930
King of Xuecang,

130
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,840
if you surrender,

131
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:54,680
I

132
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,970
can spare your life.

133
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,840
I am the king of this country.

134
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:01,120
How can I watch my people die on the battlefield

135
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,320
and live in disgrace?

136
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,800
Today,

137
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,690
even if Xuecang cannot escape this disaster,

138
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,640
I will fight to the death

139
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,040
and never be a prisoner of Yunqiu.

140
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,130
King of Xuecang,

141
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,920
you are indeed brave.

142
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,840
Then I

143
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,960
will grant your wish.

144
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,640
I advise you

145
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,940
to speak up quickly

146
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,600
so you can suffer less.

147
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,890
And we can go back and report early.

148
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,880
I know nothing about this.

149
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,450
His Majesty has decreed

150
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:55,410
that I won't be punished until the First Prince wakes up.

151
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,320
What?

152
00:09:57,640 --> 00:10:00,240
Are you trying to extort a confession by torture?

153
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,520
You are just a lowly slave.

154
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,920
You aren't dreaming that

155
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:05,200
the First Prince will come to save you, are you?

156
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:05,800
Hold on.

157
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,730
Aunt Huixin,

158
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,650
you're here.

159
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,040
Consort Yu

160
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,680
sent me to check on this girl.

161
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,900
She is the First Prince's person.

162
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,740
How dare you bully her at will?

163
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,760
You are right.

164
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,020
We will take our leave.

165
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:24,680
Go. Hurry.

166
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,760
Are you here to save me,

167
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,800
or to kill me?

168
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,480
I am here,

169
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,320
of course, on behalf of Her Highness,

170
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,880
to silence you completely.

171
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,260
Greetings, First Prince.

172
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,000
I heard you were seriously injured.

173
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,930
Why are you here?

174
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,320
You talk too much.

175
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:50,640
Tingfeng.

176
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,210
Wait for me here.

177
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:56,620
Your Highness.

178
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,420
This...

179
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,780
Your Highness.

180
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,120
You are heavily injured.

181
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,780
You shouldn't have come here.

182
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,940
Your Highness.

183
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,040
Did they torture you?

184
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,600
You came just in time, Your Highness.

185
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,680
I haven't been tortured yet.

186
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,080
Good.

187
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,810
It seems Princess Pingle is right before my eyes.

188
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,250
So Your Highness

189
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,480
knew it all along.

190
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,250
Qi Beiyi accused you

191
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,640
out of desperation.

192
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,000
You could have found a place

193
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,860
where no one knows you to recover.

194
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:12,400
Why risk your life to enter my Yunqiu Palace?

195
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:15,760
As a survivor of a conquered nation,

196
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,160
I wandered in a strange land.

197
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,490
I didn't expect to die here.

198
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,780
Letting the former Xuecang generals

199
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,600
see me in this wretched state

200
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:29,490
also goes against my original intention.

201
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,520
Even now,

202
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,370
you still refuse to tell the truth.

203
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,760
It sounds like you and Qi Beiyi

204
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,090
are not on the same side.

205
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,320
And you went through so much trouble

206
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,680
to impersonate a maid.

207
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:47,250
That means you have another plan for revenge.

208
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:50,880
I am just a commoner.

209
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,280
I don't know what you mean

210
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,240
by revenge.

211
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,720
Why did Qi Beiyi bring troops

212
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,600
into the palace?

213
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,690
Have you figured it out?

214
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:12,920
Xuecang, Yunqiu, and Jiyu had been in a tripartite balance for years.

215
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:14,880
If there were no traitors coordinating from within,

216
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:17,320
how could Xuecang, which was easy to defend and hard to attack,

217
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,720
have our army at its gates overnight

218
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,930
and even be hastily destroyed?

219
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,500
Do you think it's reasonable?

220
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,740
After Qi Beiyi betrayed Xuecang,

221
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:33,920
he indeed expected high positions and generous rewards.

222
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:34,920
But my father

223
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,520
would never employ someone

224
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,580
who betrays their country for glory.

225
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,690
He didn't expect

226
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,850
my father to go back on his word.

227
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:45,800
So he led troops into the palace last night.

228
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:47,360
And you,

229
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,360
planned everything.

230
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,120
You wanted to lurk in the palace,

231
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:54,720
but unexpectedly ran into Qi Beiyi last night.

232
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:56,080
Your true target

233
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,640
is my father.

234
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,880
You want to kill him

235
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,840
to comfort the dead soldiers.

236
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,940
Doesn't he deserve to die?

237
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,810
Killing him a hundred times

238
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:11,760
It won't bring back

239
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:15,120
the thousands of Xuecang people who have died.

240
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,360
What is your plan?

241
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:26,890
Do you also want to lead troops into the forbidden palace

242
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:30,040
and imitate what Qi Beiyi did today?

243
00:14:36,640 --> 00:14:38,370
What about you, Your Highness?

244
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:42,520
You knew my true identity long ago,

245
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:45,420
yet you still kept me by your side.

246
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,400
What is your plan then?

247
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,320
What could I plan?

248
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:52,050
I am protecting you.

249
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,320
It's useless.

250
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,210
With all that you have planned,

251
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:04,170
don't you know the result will be like last night?

252
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,080
No one can kill my father.

253
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,260
Your Highness.

254
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:14,960
I did think about

255
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:18,490
finding a chance to assassinate His Majesty.

256
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,640
But I have given up that thought now.

257
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,160
Besides,

258
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,160
I am all alone

259
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:27,130
and cannot have any plan at all.

260
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:30,280
I will not let my imagination run wild anymore.

261
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,040
At this point,

262
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:40,520
how can I trust you again?
